Make a donation to City Harvest with a Delivery.com order! You can help those in need by choosing items from the City Harvest menu. The total cost of your order will be sent as a donation to City Harvest, and help in their efforts to feed NYC's hungry. Upon receipt of your donation, you will be sent an acknowledgment letter from City Harvest.
City Harvest, the world's first and New York City's only food rescue organization, connects good food that would otherwise go to waste with people struggling with hunger. This year they will rescue 28 million pounds of food, helping to feed more than 300,000 men, women and children each week.This order will go directly to City Harvest as a monetary donation. restaurant.description: A classic New York deli that gives Kosher food justice. Traditional kosher fare that could rival any Jewish grandmother's home cooked goods as well as other more modern food means that no matter how you order, you will fall in love with 2nd Ave Deli.
